Enhancement: Add resuming from aborted backups

Restic always used re-read all files if a backup was aborted and 
restarted after.
This is now changed such that files in already saved directories will
only be re-read if they are changed between the backup runs.

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/2280
https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/3230
https://forum.restic.net/t/quicker-interrupted-backup-resumption/3470
